Usage: addHierInst [-help] -cell <cellName> [-moduleBased <parentModuleName>] {-hinst <hinstName> | -module <moduleName>}

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>                    # Name of cell (string, required)
-hinst <hinstName>                  # Name of hierarchical instance
                                    # (string, optional)
-module <moduleName>                # Name of hierarchical instance
                                    # (string, optional)
-moduleBased <parentModuleName>     # Name of module (string, optional)